sses. All functional acceptance criteria satisfied; visual criterion for toast styling fails. T14 added. Overall Status reverted to IN_PROGRESS.\n- **[2026-03-17 20:10]** (Iteration 9) fix: T14 — Fixed 6 CSS class mismatches in NotificationToast.tsx. Card box: notif-toast-row → notif-toast (and critical variant). Container: notif-toast-stack → notif-toast-list. App label: notif-row-app → notif-toast-app. Dismiss button: notif-dismiss-btn → notif-toast-close. Summary: notif-row-summary → notif-toast-summary. Body: notif-row-body → notif-toast-body. All target classes are defined in _notifications.scss. Toast popups will now receive chamfered clip-path, high-alpha background (rgba 28,31,43,0.92), and correct jewel-tone accent colors. All tasks completed — setting COUNCIL_PENDING.\n- **[2026-03-17]** (Council Iter 10) fix: Council review found 1 gap. 1 new task added (T15). All 12 functional acceptance criteria verified as satisfied. Gap: Technical Constraint \"document swaync removal in README\" was never addressed — README.md has no AGS section and no swaync mention across any of the 9 prior iterations. T15 added (medium priority). Overall Status reverted to IN_PROGRESS.\n","numLines":44,"startLine":1,"totalLines":44}}}
